title: Episode 7 - We Should’ve Gone To Sports Authority
itunes:title: Episode 7 - We Should’ve Gone To Sports Authority
description:
The Doughertys have been on the run for over a week and have managed to evade capture by laying low and traveling through 16 states undetected by law enforcement but a miscalculation on their part may prove to be their biggest mistake.
